Text: Happy New YearJeff Happy New Year I hope that all is well with you and that you are enjoying your new house I heard from Merritt that it looks fantastic No surprise there How is life outside of work Any plans to come to Europe anytime soon Any chance of seeing you in Stockholm or Copenhagen Business here is moving along much to my surprise We have raised the initial money we need to open our first stores and are trying to raise the remainder of the money we need to close out our first round of financing I had hoped that we would sign our first lease before the end of the but it looks like we will sign sometime very soon Locations should follow very soon thereafter Let me know when you will be in Europe next Hope all is well and look forward to seeing you soon Take care Adam
